Package com.vmware.appliance

The com.vmware.appliance package provides interfaces for managing vCenter Appliance configuration.

See: Description

Package com.vmware.appliance Description

The com.vmware.appliance package provides interfaces for managing vCenter Appliance configuration. The package is available starting in vSphere 6.5.
